e7d91ab183bed00" level="file"><did><unittitle>Letters Herbert received</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1991-06/1991-10" type="inclusive">June-October 1991</unitdate><container id="aspace_123afc56a8b736dac379a7f5a0b0a4f9" label="Mixed Materials [31924065338067]" type="box">12</container><container id="aspace_1bcb0c586098841f685db804cd1f71a2" parent="aspace_123afc56a8b736dac379a7f5a0b0a4f9" type="folder">12-16</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_31c705dd2ac658ad7fdb3f900fd99747"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>While not technically Joyce's, these letters bear witness to the love people had for her and the impact she had on them. As with subseries two, the cards with no personal messages were not saved, the letters are arranged alphabetically and the sheets have been numbered. October was an arbitrary cut - off date</p><list type="deflist"><defitem><label>1</label><item>Form letter reply</item></defitem><defitem><label>2</label><item>AAUW</item></defitem><defitem><label>3</label><item>Kimberly Ackley</item></defitem><defitem><label>4</label><item>Louise Adams</item></defitem><defitem><label>5</label><item>Molly Adams</item></defitem><defitem><label>6</label><item>Kit and Haraln Banks</item></defitem><defitem><label>7</label><item>Dede and Tom Bennett</item></defitem><defitem><label>8</label><item>Mart Berens</item></defitem><defitem><label>9</label><item>Barbara and Christian Boissonnas</item></defitem><defitem><label>10</label><item>Janet Bonebrake</item></defitem><defitem><label>11</label><item>Ellen Bonn</item></defitem><defitem><label>12</label><item>Jane Brentlinger</item></defitem><defitem><label>13</label><item>Charlotte Bruce</item></defitem><defitem><label>14</label><item>Sarah Brumberg</item></defitem><defitem><label>15</label><item><emph render="italic">Lynn Cagle</emph></item></defitem><defitem><label>17</label><item>Rich Calkins</item></defitem><defitem><label>18</label><item>George and Ann Calvert</item></defitem><defite